title: Why can't I make a post in Player Recruitment?

replies.body: Your profile might not have been sync'd up yet.  If this is still happening, the [syncing tool](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool) should fix things up!
Someone, please comment if you know the problem or feel like playing league of legends with me :D
